data.title: Al Massaleh Real Estate Co.
data.meta_description:
Al Massaleh Real Estate Co. | 2,163 followers on LinkedIn. Al Massaleh Real Estate is a leading real estate group with head quarters in Kuwait. The group has diverse investments in landmark projects, both residential and commercial.

Al Massaleh business units offer a wide spectrum of professional services encompassing real estate development and hospitality management, including hotels and health clubs.
